snippet.title: Tears of Themis Closed Beta Registration has begun! First Official PV(CHS Dubbing Version) Launched!
snippet.description:
❤ Register now to experience the game before the official release: 
https://tot.mihoyo.com/CBTsign-up/

❤ CHS CV info:
Titus Jin as Luke Pearce
Zhao Lu as Artem Wing
Jiang Guangtao as Vyn Richter
Yang Tianxiang as Marius von Hagen
